---
title: Indian Eggplant, Green Bean & Chicken Biryani with Yoghurt & Mint
description: A biryani sounds like just the thing to finish off the day and there’s no veggie around that can beat roasted eggplant. Don’t tell the other biryani’s out there, but this one is our new favourite!

*We've replaced the green
beans in this recipe with
courgette due to local
ingredient availability. It'll
be just as delicious, just
follow your recipe card!*
